Trade/Device Name(s): ELITech Clinical Systems GLUCOSE HK SL
Instrument(s)/Platform(s): ELITech Clinical Systems Selectra Pro Series Analyzers
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for ELITech Clinical Systems GLUCOSE HK SL reagent, calibrator, and controls for quantitative in vitro glucose measurement in serum, plasma, and urine on ELITech Clinical Systems analyzers
Indications for Use Summary: Quantitative in vitro diagnostic determination of glucose in human serum, plasma, and urine using ELITech Clinical Systems Selectra Pro Series Analyzers; calibrator and controls for calibration and quality control of ELITech Clinical Systems methods.
